* 2 Cups Baby Spinach
* 1/3 Cup Canned Kidney Beans (or any beans)

* 1 Mini Cucumber Sliced
* 4 Cherry Tomatoes Quartered
* 2 Tbsp Honey Mustard Vinaigrette (or whatever you like)
* 6-8 Croutons (optional)

Plate everything in order listed above and enjoy!

Winged Eyeliner Tutorial 👁️ 

🕊Dip eyeliner brush into eyeliner pot 
🕊Angle brush from the corner of eye, to tail of eyebrow & lightly draw upward. 
🕊Line the outer third of your eyelid (creating a very flat V shape)
🕊Fill in the crevice of the V to smooth & connect the two points
🕊Blend line into the middle of your eye, or to inner corner for a bolder look. 
🕊Repeat the process on your other eye.

* 1/2 cup white vinegar (apple cider vinegar works too)
* 1/2 cup water
* 1 tablespoons sugar (or maple syrup)
* 1 teaspoon salt
* Optional flavor boosters: peppercorns, red pepper flakes, garlic cloves, fresh herbs

🍴 Steps:
* Slice the red onion.
* Simmer vinegar, water, sugar, salt.
* Pack onions into jars.
* Pour pickling liquid over onions.
* Seal, shake, and refrigerate.
* Wait an hour (or longer) to let flavors mingle!
